%% Diagram: Block sync protocol — commit blocklist, upload only missing blocks
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client (Nucleus)
    participant M as Metadata service
    participant B as Block service
    participant MP as Magic Pocket
    participant N as Notification service

    Note over C: File changed locally
    C->>C: Re-chunk (CDC) and hash blocks [h1, h2', h3]

    C->>M: commit(blocklist=[h1, h2', h3])
    M->>M: Look up which hashes already exist
    M-->>C: need_blocks=[h2']  (h1, h3 are dedup hits)

    C->>B: PutBlock(h2', Broccoli-compressed bytes)
    B->>MP: store(h2', cell, bucket)
    MP-->>B: ack (replicated to ≥2 zones)
    B-->>C: 200 OK

    C->>M: commit(blocklist=[h1, h2', h3])
    M->>M: All blocks present — append SFJ row and bump JID
    M-->>C: committed, rev=N

    M->>N: publish(namespace, JID)
    N-->>C: notify other clients (cursor advanced)
